title: NFL Week 13: 'MVP Bowl' in Seattle & Updated Playoff Odds
itunes:title: NFL Week 13: 'MVP Bowl' in Seattle & Updated Playoff Odds
description:
Cynthia Frelund and Matt "Money" Smith use predictive analytics to go over updated playoff odds (with 5 weeks left) and preview an "MVP Bowl" between Carson Wentz and Russell Wilson this Sunday, as well as predicting the scores of all 15 of the games set for Sunday and Monday in Week 13 of the NFL regular season.
